Some CF firms have sought clarifications on the difference between relying on a third party and engaging an outsourced service provider to perform CDD measures . This is explained in paragraph 9 of the revised Guidelines . We would like to highlight that in an outsourcing scenario , the CF firm should clearly document the roles and responsibilities of the outsourced provider in a formal agreement . Necessary safeguards should be put in place to ensure that the outsourced service provider is carrying out its responsibilities effectively .

